## Hosting Architecture for Multi-Tenant SaaS

### The Core Problem

The Agent SDK is a long-running process, not a stateless API call. Serving hundreds of SaaS users means each user session needs isolated compute. The sandbox has no UI — your users interact with your Next.js frontend; the sandbox is headless compute behind your API routes.

